OL,3,CKendal's County Hall to be sold,
OL,4,CWestmorland and Furness Cabinet decides
OL,6,FCounty Hall in Kendal will be closed,
OL,7,Fas Westmorland and Furness Council
OL,8,Fofficially declares the building
OL,9,Fsurplus to requirements.
OL,11,FIt follows the council's decision in
OL,12,FJune 2024 to close daytoday
OL,13,Foperations at the building, so
OL,14,Fcustomer services, registrars and
OL,15,Fceremonies, council meetings and other
OL,16,Fservices are now housed at Kendal Town
OL,17,FHall and South Lakeland House. The
OL,18,Fcouncil says most residents will
OL,19,Fexperience no change to how or where
OL,20,Fthey access services.
