OL,3,CKendal's County Hall to be sold,
OL,4,CWestmorland and Furness Cabinet decides
OL,6,FThe council's Cabinet has voted to
OL,7,Fmove the archive collection still
OL,8,Fbased at County Hall to other
OL,9,Fbuildings in Cumbria.
OL,11,FCumbria Archives is a countywide
OL,12,Fservice, jointly funded by the two
OL,13,Fcouncils: Cumberland Council and
OL,14,FWestmorland and Furness Council.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
