OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1777378266
OL,3,CKendal's County Hall to be sold,
OL,4,CWestmorland and Furness Cabinet decides
OL,6,FCouncillors said they recognise the
OL,7,Fimportance of the county archives to
OL,8,Flocal people, historians and family
OL,9,Fresearchers. It says moving them to
OL,10,Fspecialist storage designed to keep
OL,11,Fthe documents safe will protect them
OL,12,Ffor generations to come.
OL,14,FSome materials will move to Barrow and
OL,15,FCarlisle archive centres and the
OL,16,Fpublic search room at Kendal Library
OL,17,Fwill reopen, but the council says
OL,18,Flonger-term decisions will not be made
OL,19,Funtil after a public consultation this
OL,20,Fyear.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
