OL,3,CKendal's County Hall to be sold,
OL,4,CWestmorland and Furness Cabinet decides
OL,6,FThe relocation means public access to
OL,7,Fthe archive will be paused for three
OL,8,Fmonths.
OL,10,FIt is part of a Strategic Asset
OL,11,FManagement Strategy 2024`2029,
OL,12,Femphasising active management of the
OL,13,Fauthority's estate and releasing
OL,14,Funderutilised assets.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
