OL,3,CKendal's County Hall to be sold,
OL,4,CWestmorland and Furness Cabinet decides
OL,6,FCounty Hall will be either transferred
OL,7,Fas a Community Asset or sold. The land
OL,8,Fto be disposed of includes:
OL,10,FThe main pay and display car park to
OL,11,Fthe rear and ancillary land will be
OL,12,Fretained by the council.
